<div class="w-full max-w-[430px] sm:max-w-sm md:max-w-md lg:max-w-lg xl:max-w-xl 2xl:max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-fp-body-bg flex flex-col min-h-screen shadow-xl p-6">
  <header class="pt-12 pb-8 text-center">
    <div class="inline-block p-3 bg-fp-accent-blue rounded-full mb-4 shadow-lg">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-fp-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl text-fp-neutral-darkest text-shadow-dark">Your Trust Matters</h1>
    <p class="text-fp-neutral-text text-sm mt-2">A Quick Note on Data & Security</p>
  </header>

  <main class="flex-grow space-y-5 overflow-y-auto text-sm text-fp-neutral-text">
    <p>Welcome to Food Planner! To help you create the best meal plans and shopping lists, we'll ask for some information during onboarding, like:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5 my-3">
      <li>Your dietary goals and preferences.</li>
      <li>Number of people you're planning for.</li>
      <li>Any food allergies or sensitivities.</li>
      <li>Your approximate location (optional, for local store prices).</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-fp-neutral-darkest mt-4 mb-2">Our Promise:</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5">
      <li><strong class="text-fp-primary-green">We DO:</strong> Use your information to personalize your meal plans, estimate costs, and suggest relevant recipes.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-fp-primary-green">We DO:</strong> Anonymize and aggregate data to improve our service for everyone (e.g., average food prices in a region).</li>
      <li><strong class="text-fp-error">We DON'T:</strong> Sell your personal, identifiable data to third parties.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-fp-error">We DON'T:</strong> Track your precise location beyond what you explicitly provide for store pricing (and you can opt-out or use a general region).</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4">
      We use industry-standard security measures to protect your data. You can manage your data and preferences anytime in Settings.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      By continuing, you acknowledge our
      <% if @privacy_policy %>
        <%= link_to "Privacy Policy", legal_document_path(@privacy_policy), class: "text-fp-accent-blue underline" %>
      <% end %>
      and
      <% if @terms_of_service %>
        <%= link_to "Terms of Service", legal_document_path(@terms_of_service), class: "text-fp-accent-blue underline" %>
      <% end %>.
    </p>
  </main>

  <footer class="pt-8 pb-6">
    <%= form_with model: @profile, url: onboarding_disclosure_path, method: :patch do |form| %>
      <%= form.hidden_field :acknowledged, value: true %>
      <%= form.submit "I Understand, Let's Go!", class: "w-full text-center block font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-fp bg-fp-primary-green text-fp-white shadow-fp-cta hover:bg-fp-primary-green-dark" %>
    <% end %>
    <%= button_to "Back to Welcome Screen", back_onboarding_disclosure_path, method: :get, class: "block text-center text-xs text-fp-neutral-text-light mt-4 hover:underline w-full" %>
  </footer>
</div>
